#7
The Consciousness of l0kI~
You find yourself standing in a small chambers, which reaches unto a vast
plains, a universe upon the terra firma which the mortals and immortals tread
upon their individual paths.  Here sound eats it itself hollow, and you find
that the very hand in front of your face twists around itself in a great
cosine, whereof the matter is missing, the form remains, and light seems to
become a whole within.
 
