#8
Temple of Light~
You are walking down the main hall of the Temple of Light.  This temple is
older then anyone can remember, created for the purpose of giving the recently
deceased another chance to make better of their life.  Straight down the hall
southwards is the exit/entrace of the temple.  To the east and west doors
seperate other rooms off to the sides of this hallway.
~
